<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Your Name | Advisory</title>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
      background: #0f172a;
      color: #e2e8f0;
    }

    header {
      padding: 80px 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 40px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .subtitle {
      color: #94a3b8;
      font-size: 18px;
    }

    .cta {
      margin-top: 30px;
    }

    .cta a {
      background: #facc15;
      color: #000;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-weight: bold;
    }

    section {
      max-width: 900px;
      margin: auto;
      padding: 40px 20px;
    }

    .card {
      background: #1e293b;
      padding: 25px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      border-radius: 12px;
    }

    h2 {
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px;
      color: #94a3b8;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>

<header>
  <h1>Your Name</h1>
  <p class="subtitle">Accounting • Tax • Business Advisory</p>

  <div class="cta">
    <a href="#">Contact Me</a>
  </div>
</header>

<section>
  <div class="card">
    <h2>What I Do</h2>
    <p>
      I help business owners make better financial decisions, reduce tax risk, and understand their numbers clearly.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="card">
    <h2>Services</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Tax Planning & Compliance</li>
      <li>Cash Flow Analysis</li>
      <li>Business Advisory</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="card">
    <h2>Why Work With Me</h2>
    <p>
      Not just accounting — I focus on helping you understand and use your numbers to grow your business.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<footer>
  <p>© 2026 Your Name</p>
</footer>

</body>
</html>
